sinessinsider.com%2Fdisneyland-regrets-mistakes-to-avoid-former-employee-vip-tour-guide-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDisneyland%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20I%20think%20people%20also%20have%20a%20false%20sense%20of%20security%2C%20of%20safety%2C%20because%20nothing%20bad%20happens%20at%20Disneyland%2C%26quot%3B%20Karen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWildlife%20encounters%20and%20hiking%20accidents%20can%20happen.%20The%20Smiths%20say%20that%20it's%20important%20to%20realize%20the%20real%20hazards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20Disney%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20bad%20things%20happen%20to%20people%20in%20the%20parks%20because%20they%20are%20unaware%20of%20the%20dangers%2C%26quot%3B%20Karen%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHiking%20essentials%20can%20be%20lifesavers%20and%20can%20help%20keep%20the%20national%20parks%20clean.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Smiths%20say%20the%2011th%20essential%20is%20a%20bag%20you%20can%20deposit%20waste%20in%20while%20hiking.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662a84af23b29110d3030daa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22852%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Smiths%20say%20the%2011th%20essential%20is%20a%20bag%20you%20can%20deposit%20waste%20in%20while%20hiking.%3Cp%3EZia%20Soleil%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20many%20reasons%20that%20the%20Smiths%20love%20visiting%20the%20national%20parks%20is%20because%20they%20are%20avid%20hikers.%20Being%20hikers%2C%20they%20are%20well-versed%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nps.gov%2Farticles%2F10essentials.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3B10%20essentials%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20NPS%20advises%20any%20visitor%20to%20take%20with%20them%20when%20exploring%20a%20national%20park%2C%20including%20navigation%20tools%2C%20sun%20protection%2C%20and%20first-aid%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20they've%20seen%20many%20tourists%20make%20the%20mistake%20of%20venturing%20into%20parks%20without%20the%20essentials%20in%20tow.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftourists-visit-death-valley-during-dangerous-heatwave-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20Death%20Valley%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20Karen%20said%20they%20can't%20count%20%26quot%3Bhow%20many%20times%26quot%3B%20they've%20encountered%20other%20visitors%20without%20water%20or%20sun%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20people%20understand%20how%20dangerous%20that%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Matt%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20the%20%26quot%3B10%20essentials%2C%26quot%3B%20Matt%20and%20Karen%20also%20say%20people%20often%20make%20the%20mistake%20of%20not%20taking%20WAG%20bags%20(a%20bag%20used%20to%20transport%20human%20waste%20of%20of%20a%20wilderness%20area)%20and%20instead%20resort%20to%20going%20outdoors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20feel%20like%2C%20'Well%20it's%20the%20wilderness%2C%20I'm%20just%20going%20to%20go%20out%20of%20sight%2C'%26quot%3B%20Matt%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20here's%20the%20problem%3A%20in%20some%20places%20that%20are%20so%20popular%2C%20the%20amount%20of%20human%20waste%20really%20builds%20up.%20That's%20a%20bad%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJust%20because%20there%20are%20bears%2C%20it%20doesn't%20necessarily%20mean%20you%20need%20bear%20spray.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22If%20a%20park%20is%20home%20to%20grizzly%20bears%2C%20you%20need%20bear%20spray%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Smiths.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662a851223b29110d3030de9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20a%20park%20is%20home%20to%20grizzly%20bears%2C%20you%20need%20bear%20spray%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Smiths.%3Cp%3EJoe%20McDonald%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NPS%20recommends%20that%20tourists%20carry%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-fire-commissioner-accused-bear-spray-homeless-minding-own-business-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebear%20spray%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20only%20in%20certain%20parks%2C%20which%20Karen%20and%20Matt%20say%20not%20everyone%20realizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20actually%20a%20really%20easy%20way%20to%20remember%20it.%20If%20the%20park%20has%20grizzly%20bears%2C%20you%20need%20bear%20spray%2C%26quot%3B%20Karen%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20parks%20that%20have%20the%20black%20bears%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20bear%20spray.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20bear%20spray%20is%20recommended%2C%20ensuring%20it%20is%20easily%20accessible%20is%20crucial.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20come%20upon%20a%20bear%20and%20it's%20zipped%20inside%20your%20backpack%2C%20you're%20never%20gonna%20have%20time%20to%20take%20your%20backpack%20off%20and%20unzip%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Karen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20times%2C%20we%20literally%20carry%20it%20in%20our%20hands%2C%26quot%3B%20Matt%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDoing%20too%20much%20in%20a%20national%20park%20can%20lead%20to%20%26quot%3Bactivity%20fatigue%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20bad%20experience.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22655%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Arches%20National%20Park.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F520929afecad046b05000013%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22430%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EArches%20National%20Park%20in%20Utah.%3Cp%3EColin%20D.%20Young%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20is%20home%20to%20expansive%20national%20parks%20like%20Wrangell%E2%80%93St.%20Elias%20in%20Alaska%2C%20which%20is%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E13.2%20million%20acres%2C%20and%20Yellowstone%2C%20which%20is%20over%202%20million%20acres.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20impossible%20to%20see%20everything%20worth%20seeing%20in%20one%20visit