0thought%2C%20and%20what%20you%20can%20do%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20You%20aren't%20keeping%20savings%20separate%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20savings%20should%20be%20in%20a%20separate%20account%20from%20the%20money%20you%20use%20for%20everyday%20spending%20%E2%80%94%20a%20savings%20account%2C%20not%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-checking-accounts%5C%22%3Echecking%20account%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20you%20have%20all%20of%20your%20income%20in%20one%20account%2C%20it's%20more%20difficult%20to%20determine%20what%20to%20spend%20and%20what%20not%20to%2C%20and%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20what%20is%20actually%20being%20saved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeeping%20your%20savings%20in%20a%20separate%20account%20leaves%20it%20untouched%20and%20allows%20it%20to%20grow.%20Even%20better%3A%20Set%20up%20automatic%20deductions%20from%20your%20paycheck%20into%20your%20savings%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20actually%20have%20a%20savings%20account%20with%20a%20separate%20bank%20and%20I%20do%20not%20have%20a%20debit%20card%20for%20it.%20That%20way%2C%20I%20keep%20myself%20from%20using%20those%20funds%20unless%20it%20is%20absolutely%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EToday's%20Featured%20Savings%20Accounts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ctable%20border%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EAccount%20Name%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EAPY%20(Annual%20Percentage%20Yield)%20Accurate%20as%20of%204%2F30%2F2024%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EMinimum%20Account%20Opening%20Balance%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwestern-alliance-savings-account%5C%22%3EWestern%20Alliance%20Bank%20High-Yield%20Savings%20Premier%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E5.36%25%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%24500%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fraisin-review%5C%22%3ENexBank%20High%20Yield%20Savings%20Account%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3