20Stanford%20University%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.technologyreview.com%2F2023%2F04%2F26%2F1071407%2Fplants-air-cleaning-neoplants-genetically-modified-air-quality%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20MIT%20Tech%20Review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20solve%20that%20problem%2C%20%3Cspan%3ENeoPx%3C%2Fspan%3E%20comes%20with%20%26quot%3Bpower%20drops%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20solution%20of%20their%20engineered%20bacteria%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20replenish%20the%20plant's%20microbiome%20once%20a%20month%20and%20ensure%20that%20it's%20working%20at%20its%20maximum%20air-purifying%20capacity%2C%20similar%20to%20regularly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhonewell-hpa3300bv1-powerplus-true-hepa-air-purifier-reveiw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereplacing%20an%20air%20purifier's%20filter%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELimitations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUNC's%20Morrison%20thinks%20that%20there%20are%20other%20limitations%20to%20consider%20before%20purchasing%20%3Cspan%3ENeoPx%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20really%20matter%20how%20much%20they%20modify%20the%20plant%20or%20modify%20the%20bacteria%20in%20the%20soil%20if%20they%20can't%20get%20the%20air%20into%20and%20through%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENeoPx%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20potted%20in%20a%20biodegradable%20shell%20that's%20designed%20with%20vents%20to%20maximize%20airflow%20between%20the%20soil%20and%20the%20room%2C%20but%20Morrison%20argues%20that%20the%20airflow%20would%20still%20be%20too%20minimal%20to%20make%20a%20significant%20difference%20in%20air%20quality%20for%20the%20average%20home.%20%26quot%3BIt%20might%20actually%20remove%20some%20VOCs%2C%20it%20just%20doesn't%20remove%20very%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Torbey%20and%20Mora%20are%20confident%20in%20their%20product.%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20that%20phytoremediation%20(plants-based%20solution)%20is%20not%20an%20approach%20that%20most%20in%20the%20indoor%20air%20quality%20community%20believe%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Torbey%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20later%20email%20in%20response%20to%20Morrison's%20skepticism.%20He%20and%20his%20colleagues%20have%20built%20two%20VOC%20measurement%20rooms%20at%20their%20headquarters%20in%20Paris%2C%20which%20they%20will%20use%20to%20study%20the%20phytoremediation%20potential%20of%20their%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20be%20publishing%20this%20data%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20to%20help%20the%20world%20better%20understand%20the%20power%20of%20phytoremediation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EUnpacking%20the%20%3Cspan%3ENeoPx%3C%2Fspan%3E%20system%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224271%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20potted%20plant%20sits%20next%20to%20one%20large%20box%2C%20one%20smaller%20box%2C%20a%20small%20packet%2C%20and%20a%20beaker%20with%20a%20pipette%20against%20a%20white%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662bd5620dfb1341e9ffb253%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223692%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20NeoPx%20system%20comes%20with%20a%20marble%20queen%20pothos%20potted%20in%20a%20specially%20designed%20%26quot%3Bshell%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20six-month%20supply%20of%20power%20drops.%3Cp%3ENeoplants%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cspan%3ENeoPx%3C%2Fspan%3E%20air%20purifying%20system%20comes%20with%20a%20marble%20queen%20pothos%20plant%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpoisonous-houseplants-noah-whiteman-most-delicious-poison-book-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epopular%20species%20of%20houseplant%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhich%20serves%20as%20the%20perfect%20host%20for%20their%20VOC-eating%20bacteria%2C%20Mora%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20Mora%20and%20Torbey%20hope%20to%20expand%20Neoplants%20to%20include%20different%20types%20of%20plants%2C%20but%20for%20now%2C%20pothos%20is%20the%20only%20species%20available%20for%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cspan%3ENeoPx%3C%2Fspan%3E%20package%20includes%20the%20biodegradable%2C%20vented%20shell%2C%20which%20also%20has%20a%20built-in%20self-watering%20system.%20%26quot%3BEven%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouseplant-industry-americans-billions-die-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20who%20don't%20have%20a%20green%20thumb%20at%20all%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20very%20easily%20take%20care%20of%20this%20plant%2C%26quot%3B%20Mora%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20%24119%20package%20comes%20with%20a%20six-month%20supply%20of%20power%20drops.%20When%20they%20run%20out%2C%20customers%20can%20sign%20up%20to%20auto-replenish%20them%20for%20%2439%20every%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EStriving%20for%20sustainability%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224037%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22NeoP1%20photographed%20from%20below%2C%20showing%20the%20vents%20in%20the%20shell%20with%20pothos%20leaves%20peaking%20out%20of%20the%20top.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662bd67b10dfcda40963e56e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223339%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEvery%20part%20of%20the%20NeoPx%20air%20purifying%20system%20is%20manufactured%20in%20the%20US.%3Cp%3ENeoplants%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Mora%20and%20Torbey%2C%20the%20most%20exciting%20aspect%20of%20this%20new%20product%20is%20that%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmexico-manufacturing-jobs-trade-china-biden-immigration-labor-america-businesses-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emade%20entirely%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Even%20the%20recycled%20plastic%20and%20agricultural%20waste%20used%20to%20make%20their%20self-watering%20shell%20comes%20from%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAchieving%20this%20proved%20challenging%2C%20Mora%20said%2C%20but%20he%20and%20Torbey%20wanted%20to%20manufacture%20their%20product%20as%20close%20to%20their%20main%20