0out%20and%20buy%20my%20first%20home%20by%20November%202023.%20I%20had%20even%20saved%20up%20%2410%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20my%20boyfriend%20sent%20me%20a%20link%20to%20South%20Park%20Cottages'%20website%2C%20a%20Black-owned%20tiny%20home%20village.%20I%20absolutely%20fell%20in%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20village's%20homes%20are%20newly%20built%20with%20a%20modern%20aesthetic.%20It's%20also%20close%20to%20the%20airport%20and%20Main%20Street%20in%20downtown%20Atlanta%2C%20where%20there's%20a%20strip%20of%20black-owned%20restaurants%20and%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20put%20in%20an%20offer%20for%20a%20tiny%20home%20in%20November%202022%20and%20officially%20closed%20in%20June%202023.%20I%20own%20a%20628%20square%20foot%20home%20that%20I%20purchased%20for%20%24235%2C000%20and%20have%20a%2030-year%20fixed%20mortgage%20with%20a%20monthly%20payment%20of%20%242%2C150.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20Park%20Cottages%20afforded%20me%20the%20opportunity%20to%20buy%20my%20first%20home%20sooner%20than%20planned%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20the%20official%20stamp%20for%20adulthood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIt's%20nice%20to%20have%20a%20space%20of%20my%20own%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20applied%2C%20the%20community%20was%20still%20being%20developed%20(I%20saw%20my%20home's%20construction%20framing%20and%20trusted%20the%20developer).%20It%20gave%20me%20an%20opportunity%20to%20save%20up%20more%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20was%20even%20considered%20for%20a%20home%20at%20South%20Park%20Cottages%2C%20I%20had%20to%20be%20pre-approved%20for%20the%20full%20loan%20amount%20of%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20chose%20South%20Park%20Cottages'%20preferred%20lender%2C%20along%20with%20a%20preferred%20closing%20attorney.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lending%20process%20for%20the%20tiny%20home%20worked%20like%20a%20traditional%20mortgage%2C%20requiring%20the%20same%20paperwork%3A%20The%20lender%20wanted%20to%20see%20my%20income%20and%20bank%20statements%20from%20the%20past%20two%20years%20to%20make