he%20US%20relationship%20with%20Israel%20now%20is%20far%20more%20complicated.%20The%20conflict%20in%20Gaza%20was%20sparked%20by%20Hamas'%20terror%20attacks%20in%20October%202023%20that%20killed%20hundreds.%20Israeli%20authorities%20said%20Hamas%20fighters%20captured%20253%20people%20after%20the%20assault%20across%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20112%20of%20the%20hostages%20were%20returned%20alive%2C%20but%20dozens%20are%20still%20suspected%20to%20be%20in%20captivity%2C%20Israeli%20officials%20say.%20The%20Israeli%20government%20responded%20to%20the%20attack%20with%20an%20assault%20on%20Gaza%2C%20which%20has%20killed%20more%20than%2034%2C000%20people%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20is%20an%20important%20ally%20of%20the%20US%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20emphasized%20he's%20a%20strong%20supporter%20of%20the%20Jewish%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Biden%20is%20facing%20pressure%20from%20progressive%20and%20young%20voters%2C%20who%20blame%20him%20for%20sending%20weaponry%20to%20Israel%20as%20the%20civilian%20death%20toll%20rises%20by%20the%20thousands%20in%20Gaza.%20Biden's%20administration%2C%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20has%20pushed%20the%20Israeli%20government%20to%20allow%20more%20humanitarian%20aid%20into%20the%20region%20and%20take%20steps%20to%20avoid%20civilian%20casualties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20leader%2C%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20has%20so%20far%20largely%20brushed%20off%20Biden's%20criticism%20and%20promised%20to%20launch%20an%20offensive%20into%20Rafah%2C%20a%20city%20in%20Gaza%20where%20over%201%20million%20Palestinians%20are%20taking%20refuge.%20Netanyahu%20has%20vowed%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20cease-fire%20talks%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20have%20stalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20too%2C%20has%20the%20prospect%20of%20divesting.%20Columbia%20president%20Nemat%20%26quot%3BMinouche%26quot%3B%20Shafik%20said%20school%20leaders%20and%20students%20weren't%20able%20to%20negotiate%20an%20end%20to%20the%20protest%20and%20flatly%20shot%20down%20the%20immediate%20divestment%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20University%20will%20not%20divest%20from%20Israel%2C%20the%20University%20offered%20to%20develop%20an%20expedited%20timeline%20for%20review%20of%20new%20proposals%20from%20the%20students%20by%20the%3Cu%3E%20%3C%2Fu%3EAdvisory%20Committee%20for%20Socially%20Responsible%20Investing%2C%20the%20body%20that%20considers%20divestment%20matters%2C%26quot%3B%20Shafik%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpresident.columbia.edu%2Fnews%2Fstatement-columbia-university-president-minouche-shafik-4-29%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20on%20Monday%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20then%2C%20it's%20unclear%20how%20effective%20divestment%20would%20be%20in%20changing%20the%20school's%20finances.%20The%20Ivy's%20massive%20%2413.6%20billion%20endowment%20would%20be%20challenging%20to%20sort%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20economy%20is%20so%20global%20now%20that%20even%20if%20a%20university%20decided%20that%20they%20were%20going%20to%20instruct%20their%20dominant%20management%20groups%20to%20divest%20from%20Israel%2C%20it%20would%20be%20almost%20impossible%20to%20disentangle%2C%26quot%3B%20Nicholas%20Dirks%2C%20former%20chancellor%20of%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F04%2F30%2Fbusiness%2Fwhat-is-divestment-college-protests-israel%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20CNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDivesting%20also%20means%20another%20investor%20would%20need%20to%20purchase%20those%20stocks%2C%20ultimately%20reallocating%20who%20supports%20the%20organizations%20in%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Christopher%20Marsicano%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20at%20North%20Carolina's%20Davidson%20College%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F4%2F30%2Fdivest-from-israel-breaking-down-the-us-student-protesters-demands%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Al%20Jazeera%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20divestment%20drives%20may%20be%20more%20effective%20in%20incentivizing%20political%20%E2%80%94%20not%20economic%20%E2%80%94%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Netanyahu%20has%20already%20mentioned%20student%20protests%20at%20American%20universities%20publicly%2C%26quot%3B%20Marsicano%20told%20the%20outlet.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20clear%20that%20these%20protests%20have%20captured%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20Israeli%20government%20and%20are%20putting%20some%20pressure%20on%20stakeholders%20to%20support%20a%20cease-fire.%26quot%3B%20%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolumbia-protest-demand-israel-divest-gaza-history-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714510858000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66315b9310dfcda4096516b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolumbia-protest-demand-israel-divest-gaza-history-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%201985%2C%20Columbia%20students%20protested%20for%20the%20school%20to%20divest%20from%20South%20Africa.%20The%20recent%20outcry%20over%20Israel's%20war%20in%20Gaza%20has%20many%20similarities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22psquire%40insider.com%20(Paul%20Squire)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolumbia-protest-demand-israel-divest-gaza-history-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zendaya%20Says%20%E2%80%98Challengers%E2%80%99%20Ending%20Can%20Be%20%E2%80%98Confusing%E2%80%99%20After%20Her%20Mom%20%E2%80%98Read%20the%20Ending%20So%20Different%E2%80%99%20and%20Thought%20Tashi%20Was%20%E2%80%98Pissed%E2%80%99%20Off%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C