ighted%20toward%20oldsters%20(that%20would%20be%2035%20and%20up%2C%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20this%20survey)%20who%20are%20likely%20to%20remember%20a%20time%20when%20radio%20was%20the%20only%20way%20to%20listen%20to%20audio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20radio%20is%20still%20strong%20for%20a%20younger%20demo.%20Nielsen%20says%20it%20accounts%20for%2045%25%20of%20ad-supported%20listening%20for%2018%20to%2034-year-olds%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221816%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chart%20describing%20audio%20listening%20for%20audiences%2018-34%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66312fe7ec0c696569ff3760%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENielsen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20surprised%20by%20this%2C%20that%20may%20be%20because%20you%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20on%20the%20internet%20(thank%20you!)%20and%2For%20because%20you%20don't%20spend%20that%20much%20time%20driving.%20Because%20cars%2C%20for%20lots%20of%20people%2C%20still%20equal%20radio%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edisonresearch.com%2Fthe-infinite-dial-2024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEdison%20Research%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%2070%25%20of%20people%20who've%20been%20in%20a%20car%20in%20the%20last%20month%20are%20primarily%20listening%20to%20radio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20also%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0if%20you've%20been%20reading%20this%20closely%20(thank%20you!)%20%E2%80%94%20you%20will%20have%20also%20noticed%20that%20those%20Nielsen%20numbers%20only%20reference%20%26quot%3Bad-supported%20audio%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20means%20it's%20not%20measuring%20all%20listening.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fs29.q4cdn.com%2F175625835%2Ffiles%2Fdoc_financials%2F2024%2Fq1%2FQ1-2024-Shareholder-Deck-FINAL.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpotify%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20says%20it%20has%2064%20million%20premium%20subscribers%20in%20North%20America%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20pay%20to%20listen%20to%20on-demand%2C%20ad-free%20music.%20And%20they%20don't%20show%20up%20in%20this%20Nielsen%20survey.%20%3Cspan%3EThe%20same%20goes%20for%20Apple's%20Music%20subscribers%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20happens%20when%20you%20look%20at%20the%20way%20audio%20habits%20for%20%3Cem%3Eall%3C%2Fem%3E%20kinds%20of%20listening%20pan%20out%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENielsen's%20data%20here%20isn't%20as%20granular%20as%20I%20would%20have%20liked%2C%20but%20they%20were%20able%20to%20give%20me%20some%20sense.%20TL%3BDR%3A%20Radio%20usage%2C%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20isn't%20nearly%20as%20dominant.%20But%20it's%20still%20on%20top%3A%20Nielsen%20says%20it%20accounts%20for%2037%25%20of%20all%20listening%20time%2C%20followed%20by%20streaming%20audio%20(19%25)%2C%20podcasts%20(11%25)%2C%20and%20Sirius%20XM%20(8%25).%20(The%20remaining%2025%25%20is%20split%20every%20other%20way%20you%20can%20consume%20audio%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0stuff%20you%20own%20yourself%2C%20stuff%20you%20listen%20to%20on%20YouTube%2C%20etc.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20where%20does%20all%20of%20this%20lead%20us%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20it%20suggests%20that%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjon-stewart-daily-show-audience-old-small-tv-ratings-streaming-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunlike%20cable%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20young%2Fyoungish%20people%20haven't%20entirely%20abandoned%20radio.%20Chalk%20it%20up%2C%20most%20likely%2C%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20it's%20both%20free%20and%2C%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20still%20easier%20to%20listen%20to%20in%20a%20car%20than%20something%20delivered%20over%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20suggests%20that%20gravity%20is%20real%2C%20water%20is%20wet%2C%20and%20that%20just%20like%20you%20think%2C%20the%20more%20choices%20you%20have%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20more%20choices%20you%20are%20exposed%20to%20%E2%80%94%20the%20less%20likely%20you%20are%20to%20pick%20radio.%20Just%20like%20you%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fradio-usage-nielsen-cars-streaming-spotify-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714505158000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6631379cec0c696569ff3cc4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fradio-usage-nielsen-cars-streaming-spotify-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20internet%20is%20killing%20TV%2C%20and%20it%20will%20get%20to%20radio.%20But%20not%20quite%20yet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pkafka%40insider.com%20(Peter%20Kafka)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fradio-usage-nielsen-cars-streaming-spotify-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20Failed%20Pre-Meds%26quot%3B%3A%20Kota%20Official%20To%20Students%2C%20Parents%20As%20Suicides%20Spike%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKota%20District%20Collector%20Dr%20Ravinder%20Goswami%20wrote%20to%20the%20NEET%20and%20JEE%20aspirants%20and%20their%20parents%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20citing%20his%20own%20example%20of%20failing%20the%20Pre-Medical%20Test%20several%20years%20ago.%20His%20letters%20came%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20rising%20cases%20of%20suicides%2C%20with%20two%20incidents%20taking%20place%20within%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goswami%2C%20an%20MBBS%20doctor%20before%20he%20became%20an%20IAS%20officer%2C%20said%20a%20failure%20is%20an%20opportunity%20to%20improve%20and%20turn%20it%20into%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20urged%20the%20parents%20to%20give%20a%20chance%20to%20their%20wards%20to%20improve%20their%20mistakes%20and%20not%20associate%20happiness%20of%20the%20children%20with%20the%20marks%20they%20obtain%20in%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuoting%20a%20motivating%20couplet%20from%20Urdu%20poet%20Sahir%20Ludhianvi%2C%20Mr%20Goswami%20began%20his%20address%20to%20the%20students%2