20Alam%20after%20she%20called%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bvote%20jihad%26quot%3B%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20candidate%20from%20Farrukhabad%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeking%20votes%20for%20INDIA%20bloc%20candidate%20Naval%20Kishore%20Shakya%20on%20Monday%2C%20Ms%20Alam%2C%20a%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20leader%2C%20made%20an%20appeal%20for%20%26quot%3Bvote%20jihad%26quot%3B%2C%20terming%20it%20as%20necessary%20in%20the%20current%20situation%20for%20the%20minority%20community%20to%20drive%20away%20the%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20cognisance%20of%20the%20remarks%20made%20by%20Maria%20Alam%2C%20a%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20her%20for%20violating%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20IPC%20and%20Representation%20of%20People%20Act%20following%20a%20complaint%20made%20by%20the%20Flying%20Squad%20and%20Surveillance%20Team%2C%20police%20said%2C%20and%20added%20that%20a%20case%20was%20also%20registered%20against%20Mr%20Khurshid%2C%20who%20was%20the%20chief%20guest%20at%20the%20election%20meeting%20in%20Kaimganj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SHO%20of%20Kaimganj%20police%20station%2C%20Ramautar%2C%20on%20Tuesday%20told%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20Maria%20Alam%20and%20Salman%20Khurshid%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20complaint%20made%20by%20the%20Flying%20Squad%20and%20Surveillance%20Team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20case%20was%20registered%20under%20sections%20188%20(disobedience%20to%20order%20duly%20promulgated%20by%20public%20servant)%2C%20295A%20(deliberate%20and%20malicious%20acts%2C%20intended%20to%20outrage%20religious%20feelings%20of%20any%20class%20by%20insulting%20its%20religion%20or%20religious%20beliefs)%20of%20the%20IPC%20and%20section%20125%20(promoting%20enmity%20between%20classes%20in%20connection%20with%20election)%20of%20the%20Representation%20of%20People%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTogether%20do%20vote%20jihad%20--%20with%20intelligence%2C%20without%20being%20sentimental%20and%20with%20silence.%20As%20we%20can%20only%20do%20vote%20jihad%20to%20drive%20away%20this%20Sanghi%20government.%26quot%3B%20Stressing%20that%20it%20was%20time%20to%20join%20hands%2C%20she%20said%20otherwise%20this%20%26quot%3BSanghi%20government%20will%20succeed%20in%20wiping%20out%20our%20existence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20say%20that%20Constitution%20and%20democracy%20are%20under%20threat.%20But%20I%20say%20that%20insaniyat%20(humanity)%20is%20under%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20there%20is%20an%20attack%20on%20'insaniyat'.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20save%20the%20country%2C%20its%20beauty%20and%20'ganga-jamuni'%20(composite)%20culture%2C%20then%20vote%20very%20intelligently%20without%20getting%20influenced%20by%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20of%20Ms%20Alam's%20statement%20has%20also%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20statement%20of%20his%20niece%2C%20Mr%20Khurshid%20said%20generally%20he%20avoids%20using%20such%20words%20because%20its%20literal%20meaning%20is%20misinterpreted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJihad%20means%20to%20fight%20against%20a%20situation.%20Her%20intention%20must%20have%20been%20to%20carry%20out%20vote%20jihad%20to%20protect%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20candidature%20from%20INDIA%20bloc%20from%20the%20Farrukhabad%20seat%2C%20Mr%20Khurshid%20said%20he%20was%20offered%20a%20Congress%20ticket%20from%20Aligarh.%20But%20he%20politely%20declined%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20Salman%20Khurshid%20from%20Farrukhabad%20and%20I%20stay%20that%20only%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20first%20public%20meeting%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20in%20Farrukhabad%20with%20most%20of%20the%20senior%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20SP%20present%20together%20on%20the%20dias.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Ex