by%20Khalistanis%20from%20Canada%2C%20it%20was%20inconceivable%20that%20a%20national%20party%20would%20stoop%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20expect%20the%20elements%20in%20Canada%20to%20do%20this.%20I%20expect%20people%20in%20Pakistan%20to%20do%2C%20I%20expect%20people%20in%20the%20northern%20country%20to%20do%20this.%20But%20I%20would%20have%20never%20thought%20that%20in%20such%20a%20brazen%20manner%2C%20a%20national%20political%20party%20would%20get%20so%20desperate%20that%20they%20will%20also%20start%20editing%20videos%20and%20distorting%20the%20truth%20to%20push%20a%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20why%20he%20thinks%20it%20is%20a%20strategy%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20minister%20cited%20an%20incident%20in%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%20in%20Kerala%2C%20a%20Congress%20party%20worker%20morphed%20an%20image%20of%20me%20along%20with%20somebody%20else%2C%20to%20do%20something%20that%20is%20absolutely%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20misinformation%20and%20life.%20So%20this%20is%20not%20some%20isolated%20incident%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20pattern.%20And%20this%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20concerted%20strategy%20on%20part%20of%20the%20Congress%20because%20they%20are%20left%20with%20no%20other%20option%20but%20to%20lie%20their%20way%20and%20gain%20some%20votes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20persons%20--%20one%20of%20them%20from%20Gujarat%20--%20have%20already%20been%20arrested%20for%20the%20doctored%20video%20that%20tried%20to%20show%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20saying%20he%20would%20remove%20reservations%20--%C2%A0%20which%20the%20Congress%20alleges%20is%20a%20BJP%20plan%2C%20to%20be%20implemented%20if%20they%20achieving%20the%20targetted%20400-majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20also%20summoned%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20Revanth%20Reddy%20for%20questioning%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20national%20election%2C%20the%20video%20was%20allegedly%20shared%20by%20the%20official%20X%20handle%20of%20Telangana%20Congress%2C%20after%20which%20many%20party%20leaders%20re-posted%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deep-fake%20video%20attempted%20to%20portray%20Mr%20Shah%20talking%20about%20scrapping%20all%20reservations%2C%20while%20he%20was%20actually%20referring%20to%20removing%20quota%20only%20for%20Muslims%20on%20religious%20grounds%20in%20Telangana.%20The%20BJP%20had%20scrapped%20such%20a%20quota%20in%20Karnataka%20before%20it%20lost%20power%20to%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20press%20conference%20later%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20played%20both%20videos%20to%20show%20what%20he%20actually%20said%20and%20what%20the%20doctored%20content%20projected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeclaring%20that%20the%20people%20involved%20will%20be%20have%20to%20face%20action%2C%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bshocking%20is%20that%20there%20is%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20who%20is%20party%20to%20it%20and%20there%20is%20a%20national%20party%20or%20the%20oldest%20national%20party%2C%20party%20to%20it%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714500120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F6j17mfr8_rajeev-chandrasekhar-650_625x300_31_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-expect-pak-but-a-national-party-minister-on-congress-amid-video-row-5559971%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20Rajeev%20Chansekhar%20said%20today%20that%20the%20deep%20fake%20video%20on%20his%20cabinet%20colleague%20Amit%20Shah%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeliberate%20violation%20of%20the%20law%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Congress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-expect-pak-but-a-national-party-minister-on-congress-amid-vi