ame%20family%20and%20tried%20to%20strip%20her%2C%20but%20failed%20because%20she%20was%20holding%20on%20tightly%20to%20her%20young%20granddaughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20managed%20to%20escape%20the%20clutches%20of%20the%20mob%20after%20the%20group%20attacking%20her%20went%20towards%20the%20first%20two%20survivors%20-%20one%20in%20her%2040s%20and%20the%20other%20in%20her%2020s%20-%20who%20were%20being%20attacked%20in%20some%20paddy%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20women%20had%20sought%20the%20help%20of%20police%20personnel%20present%20at%20the%20spot%2C%20but%20were%20left%20at%20the%20mob's%20mercy%2C%20the%20agency%20said%20in%20the%20chargesheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeavily%20Armed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20the%20women%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20was%20the%20wife%20of%20a%20Kargil%20war%20veteran%2C%20pleaded%20with%20the%20police%20personnel%20to%20drive%20them%20to%20a%20safe%20location%20but%20were%20allegedly%20told%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20was%20no%20key%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20vehicle.%20They%20later%20drove%20them%20right%20to%20the%20mob%20and%20refused%20to%20go%20any%20further%2C%20the%20chargesheet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20filed%20its%20chargesheet%20against%20six%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20and%20a%20report%20against%20a%20child%20in%20conflict%20with%20the%20law%20(CCL)%20before%20the%20Special%20CBI%20judge%20in%20Guwahati%20on%20October%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20states%20that%20the%20mob%20that%20the%20women%20were%20running%20from%20was%20900-1%2C000%20people%20strong%20and%20many%20of%20its%20members%20carried%20sophisticated%20weapons%20like%20AK%2C%20SLR%2C%20INSAS%20and%20.303%20rifles.%20The%20mob%20allegedly%20%26quot%3Bburnt%20to%20the%20ground%26quot%3B%20all%20the%20houses%20of%20the%20women's%20village%2C%20B%20Phainom%20in%20Kangpokpi%20district%2C%20after%20vandalising%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGroup%20Split%20Up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20village%20was%20being%20ransacked%2C%20the%20three%20women%20and%20seven%20others%20ran%20into%20the%20Haokhongching%20forest%20nearby%20to%20hide%20from%20the%20mob%2C%20but%20were%20spotted.%20One%20group%20from%20the%20mob%20took%20two%20men%20and%20two%20women%20with%20them%2C%20another%20captured%20the%20third%20victim%20and%20her%20granddaughter%20while%20the%20third%20took%20the%20village%20chief%2C%20another%20man%20and%20his%20two%20daughters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chargesheet%20states%20that%20one%20of%20the%20two%20women%20who%20was%20gang-raped%20and%20paraded%20naked%20was%20unwell%20and%20had%20to%20be%20carried%20on%20the%20backs%20of%20male%20members%20of%20the%20family%20as%20they%20proceeded%20to%20the%20Chakhama%20village%2C%20which%20is%20about%20four%20km%20from%20theirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mob's%20ranks%20swelled%20as%20others%20from%20a%20nearby%20village%20joined%20the%20group%20and%20all%20of%20them%20started%20thrashing%20the%20victims.%20At%20this%20time%2C%20some%20people%20in%20the%20mob%20told%20the%20women%20there%20was%20a%20police%20vehicle%20parked%20near%20the%20road%20and%20they%20should%20go%20there%20and%20seek%20help%2C%20officials%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20the%20two%20women%20and%20a%20man%20managed%20to%20get%20inside%20the%20vehicle%2C%20a%20Gypsy%2C%20in%20which%20two%20police%20personnel%20and%20a%20driver%20were%20sitting%20while%20three%20to%20four%20personnel%20stood%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20pleaded%20with%20the%20driver%20to%20take%20them%20to%20a%20safe%20place%20but%20was%20told%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20was%20no%20key%26quot%3B.%20Later%2C%20the%20driver%20drove%20the%20Gypsy%20straight%20to%20the%20mob%20and%20stopped%20it%20in%20front%20of%20them.%20The%20victims%20begged%20the%20police%20personnel%20to%20drive%20them%20to%20safety%2C%20but%20to%20no%20avail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMan%20In%20Vehicle%20Killed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violent%20mob%20headed%20toward%20the%20vehicle%20and%20the%20police%20personnel%20fled.%20By%20this%20time%2C%20the%20rioters%20had%20already%20killed%20the%20father%20of%20the%20man%20who%20was%20sitting%20in%20the%20Gypsy%20and%20he%20was%20also%20later%20bludgeoned%20to%20death%2C%20the%20CBI%20chargesheet%20stated.%20Their%20bodies%20were%20thrown%20on%20a%20dry%20riverbed%20near%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20survivors%20were%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20Gypsy%2C%20stripped%20and%20paraded%20naked.%20They%20were%20later%20gang-raped.%20The%20third%20woman%2C%20%26quot%3Bcrying%20inconsolably%26quot%3B%2C%20ran%20towards%20another%20village%20and%20was%20reunited%20with%20her%20family%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20has%20chargesheeted%20Huirem%20Herodas%20Meitei%2C%20Arun%20Kungongbam%2C%20Ningombam%20Tomba%20Singh%2C%20Yumlemban%20Jiban%20Singh%2C%20Pukrihongbam%20Surunjoy%20Meiti%20and%20Nameirakpam%20Kiran%20Meiti%20and%20a%20report%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20a%20juvenile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvestigation%20has%20established%20that%20the%20accused%20individuals%2C%20part%20of%20ethnic%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20Kukis%2C%20conspired%20with%20a%20large%20group%20of%20unidentified%20miscreants%20from%20the%20Meitei%20community%20to%20execute%20a%20series%20of%20preplanned%20criminal%20acts%2C%20including%20violence%2C%20arson%2C%20sexual%20assault%2C%20and%20murder%20with%20a%20clear%20intent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chargesheet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20deliberate%20actions%20which%20specifically%20targeted%20victims%20from%20the%20tribal%20community%2C%20included%20threats%2C%20violence%20and%20various%20unlawful%20acts%2C%20aimed%20at%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20have%20been%20charged%20under%20various%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20including%20those%20pertaining%20to%20gang%20rape%2C%20murder%2C%20outraging%20the%20modesty%20of%20a%20woman%20and%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20the%20CBI%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714499940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F1ovnf21o_manipur-crime-ndtv-650_650x400_20_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomen-paraded-raped-in-manipur-were-driven-to-mob-by-cops-cbi-chargesheet-5560033%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20shocking%20charge%2C%20the%20CBI%20has%20alleged%20that%20personnel%20from%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20allegedly%20drove%20the%20two%20women%20to%20a%20mob%20of%20around%201%2C000%20people%2C%20which%20stripped%20and%20paraded%20them%20before%20they%20were%20gang-raped%2C%20in%20an%20incident%20that%20shook%20the%20nation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomen-paraded-raped-in-manipur-were-driven-to-mob-by-cops-cbi-chargesheet-5560033%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomen-paraded-raped-in-manipur-were-driven-to-mob-by-cops-cbi-chargesheet-5560033%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomen-paraded-raped-in-manipur-were-driven-to-mob-by-cops-cbi-chargesheet-5560033%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IPL%202024%3A%20Stoinis%2C%20Mohsin%20Guide%20LSG%20To%20Win%3B%20MI's%20Playoff%20Dreams%20In%20Trouble%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELSG%20vs%20MI%20IPL%202024%2C%20Highlights%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0Marcus%20Stoinis%20slammed%20a%20brilliant%20half-century%20to%20guide%20LSG%20to%20a%20four-wicket%20win%20over%20MI.%20Hardik%20Pandya%20took%20two%20wickets%20for%20MI..%20Earlier%2C%20Nehal%20Wadhera%20scored%20a%20gritty%2046%20to%20take%20MI%20to%20144%2F7.%20For%20LSG%2C%20Mohsin%20Khan%20took%20two%20wickets%20while%20M