%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fexternal-affairs-defence-security%2Fnews%2Fwhy-a-chinese-company-s-monopoly-may-pose-a-security-risk-at-indian-ports-124043001232_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fexternal-affairs-defence-security%2Fnews%2Fwhy-a-chinese-company-s-monopoly-may-pose-a-security-risk-at-indian-ports-124043001232_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%203rd%20To%206th%20Phase%2C%20Polls%20To%20Anantnag-Rajouri%20Constituency%20Deferred%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20elections%20to%20the%20redrawn%20Anantnag-Rajouri%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20which%20was%20slated%20to%20go%20to%20polls%20on%20May%207%20(third%20phase)%2C%20has%20been%20deferred%20to%20May%2025%20(sixth%20phase)%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20after%20several%20political%20parties%20of%20the%20Union%20Territory%20requested%20to%20shift%20the%20date%20due%20to%20logistic%20and%20connectivity%20issues%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20leaders%20including%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20BJP%20unit%20chief%20Ravinder%20Raina%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Apni%20Party%20chief%20Altaf%20Bukhari%2C%20People's%20Conference%20leader%20Imran%20Ansari%20and%20others%20had%20approached%20the%20Election%20Commission%20requesting%20for%20rescheduling%20of%20polls%20to%20the%20seat%20due%20to%20adverse%20weather%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVarious%20representations%20have%20been%20received%20from%20different%20political%20parties%20of%20the%20UT%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20for%20shifting%20the%20date%20of%20poll%20of%20election%20from%203-Anantnag-Rajouri%20Parliamentary%20Constituency%20due%20to%20various%20logistic%2C%20communication%20and%20natural%20barrier%20of%20of%20connectivity%20turning%20out%20as%20hindrance%20in%20campaigning%20which%20in%20turn%20tantamount%20to%20lack%20of%20fair%20opportunities%20for%20the%20contesting%20candidates%20which%20may%20affect%20the%20poll%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20poll%20body%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20said%20that%20after%20considering%20a%20report%20from%20the%20administration%20and%20analysing%20the%20ground%20situation%20in%20the%20constituency%2C%20it%20decided%20to%20revise%20the%20date%20of%20the%20poll%20under%20Section%2056%20of%20the%20Representation%20of%20People%20Act%2C%201951.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20other%20statutory%20processes%20including%20%26quot%3Bnomination%2C%20scrutiny%20and%20withdrawal%20are%20already%20over%20with%2020%20contesting%20candidates.%20Except%20poll%20date%2C%20no%20changes%20in%20any%20part%20of%20the%20schedule%2C%26quot%3B%20sources%20in%20the%20Election%20Commission%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20is%20the%20first%20major%20poll%20since%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370%20in%202019%20which%20bifurcated%20the%20state%20into%20two%20union%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chief%20Ministers%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Omar%20Abdullah%20(National%20Conference)%20and%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20(PDP)%20had%20urged%20the%20Election%20Commission%20last%20week%20not%20to%20postpone%20the%20polls.Interestingly%2C%20BJP%20and%20People's%20Conference%20who%20had%20demanded%20deferment%20of%20polls%20are%20not%20contesting%20in%20Anantnag-Rajouri.%20Now%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20likely%20to%20back%20the%20Apni%20Party%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20parties%20are%20struggling%20with%20the%20new%20electoral%20map%20of%20the%20Anantnag%20constituency%20as%20the%20delimitation%20has%20drastically%20redrawn%20electoral%20boundaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20mountains%20divide%20one%20part%20of%20the%20Anantnag%20constituency%20from%20the%20others%20in%20Rajouri%20and%20Poonch.%20In%20between%20is%20Shopian%20district%20which%20has%20been%20made%20part%20of%20the%20Srinagar%20seat%20-%20leading%20to%20a%20geographical%20disconnect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20thrown%20some%20serious%20challenges%20at%20the%20parties%20who%20need%20to%20campaign%20in%20two%20disconnected%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20polls%20will%20decide%20the%20fate%20of%2020%20candidates%2C%20including%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20who%20is%20facing%20a%20challenge%20from%20National%20Conference%20leader%20Mian%20Altaf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20in%20Udhampur%20was%20held%20on%20April%2019%2C%20in%20Jammu%20on%20April%2026%2C%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20it%20will%20be%20on%20May%2013%2C%20in%20Baramulla%20on%20May%2020%20and%20Anantnag-Rajouri%20on%20May%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714493280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fklr4bqh4_anantnag_625x300_30_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-from-3rd-to-6th-phase-polls-to-anantnag-rajouri-constituency-deferred-5559274%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20elections%20to%20the%20redrawn%20Anantnag-Rajouri%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20which%20was%20slated%20to%20go%20to%20polls%20on%20May%207%20(third%20phase)%2C%20has%20been%20deferred%20to%20May%2025%20(sixth%20phase)%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-from-3rd-to-6th-phase-polls-to-anantnag-rajouri-constituency-deferred-5559274%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-from-3rd-to-6th-phase-polls-to-anantnag-rajouri-constituency-deferred-5559274%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-from-3rd-to-6th-phase-polls-to-anantnag-rajouri-constituency-deferred-5559274%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Revealed%3A%20How%20India's%20T20%20WC-Bound%20Stars%20Fared%20In%20IPL%20-%20Concern%20Over%20Pandya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20likes%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ro