n%3Cp%3EFour%20candidates%20have%20been%20named%20in%20the%20fresh%20list%20and%20they%20include%20actor-turned-politician%20Raj%20Babbar%20from%20the%20Gurgaon%20constituency%20and%20former%20Union%20Minister%20Anand%20Sharma%20from%20the%20Kangra%20constituency%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Babbar%20will%20contest%20against%20BJP%20veteran%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Rao%20Inderjit%20Singh.%20With%20the%20announcement%20of%20his%20candidature%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20revealed%20the%20names%20of%20all%20nine%20candidates%20it%20is%20fielding%20from%20Haryana%2C%20where%20the%20tenth%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20is%20being%20contested%20by%20its%20INDIA%20ally%2C%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharma%2C%20who%20is%20making%20his%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20debut%2C%20is%20up%20against%20the%20BJP's%20Rajeev%20Bhardwaj%2C%20a%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%20Kangra%20Central%20Cooperative%20(KCC)%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20MLA%20Satpal%20Raizada%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20the%20Hamirpur%20constituency%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20an%20uphill%20battle%20because%20he%20will%20be%20facing%20off%20against%20Union%20Minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%2C%20who%20has%20won%20from%20there%20four%20times.%20The%20seat%20was%20also%20held%20by%20Mr%20Thakur's%20father%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Prem%20Kumar%20Dhumal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra%2C%20where%20the%20battle%20is%20between%20the%20Congress-NCP%20(Sharad%20Pawar%20Faction)-Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction)%20and%20the%20BJP-NCP%20(Ajit%20Pawar%20faction)-Shiv%20Sena%20(Eknath%20Shinde%20faction)%2C%20the%20party%20has%20pitted%20Bhushan%20Patil%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20its%20Mumbai%20unit%2C%20against%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20debutant%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20the%20names%20declared%20for%20some%20high-profile%20constituencies%2C%20the%20list%20was%20noteworthy%20more%20for%20what%20was%20left%20out.%20The%20buzz%20had%20been%20building%20about%20the%20Congress%20finally%20pulling%20the%20trigger%20and%20deciding%20on%20the%20names%20for%20Raebareli%20and%20Amethi.%20The%20Amethi%20unit%20of%20the%20Congress%20even%20staged%20a%20protest%20earlier%20on%20Tuesday%20demanding%20that%20a%20candidate%20be%20declared%20and%20that%20the%20person%20be%20from%20the%20%26quot%3BGandhi%20parivar%20(family)%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20the%20decision%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20put%20off%20for%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20date%20for%20filing%20nominations%20for%20both%20the%20seats%2C%20which%20will%20go%20to%20the%20polls%20on%20May%2020%2C%20is%20Friday%2C%20May%203.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeculation%20has%20been%20rife%20that%20the%20party%20would%20field%20its%20former%20president%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20-%20who%20lost%20the%20family%20bastion%20in%20a%20shock%20defeat%20to%20the%20BJP's%20Smriti%20Irani%20in%202019%20-%20from%20Amethi%20again%20and%20he%20will%20contest%20both%20from%20there%20and%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%20like%20he%20did%20in%20the%20last%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Raebareli%2C%20which%20was%20held%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20since%202004%2C%20the%20name%20doing%20the%20rounds%20has%20been%20of%20Congress%20General%20Secretary%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20whose%20electoral%20debut%20is%20expected%20to%20enthuse%20party%20workers.%20The%20move%2C%20if%20it%20happens%2C%20would%20be%20strategic%20also%20because%20Raebareli%20was%20the%20only%20seat%20-%20out%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%2080%20-%20that%20the%20Congress%20had%20won%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714492800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-01%2Fdqh52igg_congress-generic_625x300_21_January_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-releases-another-poll-list-no-decision-on-amethi-raebareli-5558892%22%2C%22summary%22%