ary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109731957.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20civil%20war%20in%20Sudan%20has%20led%20to%20a%20severe%20food%20crisis%2C%20forcing%20people%20to%20resort%20to%20eating%20soil%20and%20tree%20leaves%20to%20survive.%20The%20conflict%20between%20the%20Sudanese%20army%20and%20RSF%20has%20disrupted%20agriculture%2C%20leading%20to%20widespread%20hunger%20and%20malnutrition.%20International%20aid%20efforts%20are%20hindered%20by%20looting%20and%20bureaucratic%20obstacles%2C%20putting%20many%20lives%20at%20risk.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsevere-hunger-crisis-people-in-sudan-resort-to-eating-soil-and-leaves-to-survive%2Farticleshow%2F109731957.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsevere-hunger-crisis-people-in-sudan-resort-to-eating-soil-and-leaves-to-survive%2Famp_articleshow%2F109731957.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsevere-hunger-crisis-people-in-sudan-resort-to-eating-soil-and-leaves-to-survive%2Famp_articleshow%2F109731957.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Order%20Organic%20Mangoes%20From%20Farms%20Across%20India%20Using%208%20Online%20Platforms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20remember%20rushing%20home%20from%20school%20to%20savour%20a%20bowl%20filled%20with%20fleshy%2C%20yellow%20squares%20of%20delight%3F%20I%20do.%20Summer%20afternoons%20often%20meant%20eyeing%20the%20neighbour%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Ekairi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(raw%20mango)%20trees%2C%20elated%20when%20the%20green%20beauties%20would%20fall%20to%20the%20ground%20and%20be%20almost%20immediately%20scooped%20into%20our%20baskets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20summer%20progresses%2C%20no%20Indian%20is%20a%20stranger%20to%20the%20long%20wait%20that%20ensues%20for%20the%20yellowish-green%20hues%20to%20transform%20into%20its%20ripe%20golden-orange%20form.%20And%20no%20one%20questions%20the%20long%20queues%20outside%20popular%20Gujarati%20joints%20whose%20%3Cem%3Eaamras%20puri%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20dish%20of%20sweet%20mango%20pulp%20served%20with%20deep-fried%20flatbread)%20is%20%E2%80%9Cto%20die%20for%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20the%20regulars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20juicy%20fact%20that%20summers%20in%20India%20are%20incomplete%20without%20mango%20dominating%20our%20homes%20and%20palates.%20This%20comes%20as%20no%20surprise.%20Indians%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F57267%2Fmango-national-fruit-of-india-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultivating%20mangoes%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20thousands%20of%20years%2C%20and%20till%20today%2C%20the%20love%20for%20the%20fruit%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20waned%20even%20one%20bit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Alphonso%20continues%20to%20hold%20its%20status%20as%20a%20cult%20favourite%20for%20its%20vibrant%20sweetness%20and%20distinct%20flavour%2C%20there%20are%20hundreds%2C%20if%20not%20thousands%20of%20varieties%20that%20dot%20the%20landscape%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20mango%20cultivation.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20lesser-known%20varieties%20make%20an%20appearance%20in%20chutneys%2C%20pickles%20and%20the%20like%2C%20lending%20them%20their%20citrusy%20flavour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20if%20you%20haven%E2%80%99t%20got%20your%20stock%20of%20mangoes%20yet%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20a%20suggestion%3A%20why%20not%20get%20them%20delivered%20to%20you%20straight%20from%20a%20farm%3F%20We%E2%80%99ve%20put%20together%20a%20list%20of%20people%2C%20startups%20and%20local%20platforms%20that%20are%20bringing%20the%20sweetness%20of%20the%20mango%20from%20the%20tree%20to%20your%20plate.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3