0And%20no%20one%20looking%20on%20would%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20that%20just%20a%20few%20days%20back%2C%20these%20girls%20had%20been%20strangers%20to%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20what%20travel%20does%20to%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Zinal%20Doshi%2C%20leader%20of%20this%20iconic%20trek%20and%20founder%20of%20%E2%80%98The%20Flapper%20Life%E2%80%99.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334177%2Fbest-travel-startups-in-india-local-experiences-tentgram-curtain-call-adventures-not-on-map%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperiential%20travel%20platform%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20making%20solo%20travel%20possible%20for%20Indian%20women%2C%20arguably%20a%20tough%20feat%20to%20accomplish%2C%20according%20to%20Zinal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHelping%20women%20like%20Meenakshi%20realise%20their%20mettle%20is%20exactly%20what%20the%20Mumbai%20girl%20set%20out%20to%20do%20when%20she%20quit%20her%2014-year-long%20banking%20career%20to%20launch%20a%20travel%20startup%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20a%20venture%20that%20is%20breaking%20social%20constructs%20of%20solo%20travel%2C%20changing%20the%20status%20quo%20that%20once%20required%20women%20to%20have%20%E2%80%9Ccompany%20to%20feel%20safe%E2%80%9D%20and%20helping%20women%20not%20be%20so%20dismissive%20of%20themselves%2C%20is%20tough.%20But%20Zinal%20says%20there%20is%20fun%20in%20the%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConversations%20with%20friends%20and%20personal%20experience%20had%20led%20her%20to%20conclude%20that%20women%20were%20always%20%E2%80%9Cwaiting%20for%20someone%E2%80%99s%20okay%E2%80%9D%20when%20it%20came%20to%20travel.%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%20for%20their%20family%E2%80%99s%20approval%20and%20sometimes%20for%20their%20friend%E2%80%99s%20plans%20to%20sync%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20women%20do%20not%20get%20to%20travel%20when%20they%20want%20to.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5C