es-affordable-troo-good-millet-snacks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthy%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20her%20during%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Prathima%20Viswanath%20also%20went%20through%20this%20dilemma%20as%20she%20looked%20for%20different%20healthy%20recipes%20to%20give%20to%20her%20daughter%2C%20a%20tennis%20player.%20The%20Hyderabad%20resident%20accompanied%20her%20daughter%20to%20various%20African%20and%20Asian%20countries%2C%20but%20struggled%20to%20make%20food%20that%20could%20be%20carried%20for%20long%20periods%20of%20time%20%E2%80%94%20food%20that%20isn%E2%80%99t%20fried%20or%20oily%2C%20yet%20meeting%20the%20caloric%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20the%2046-year-old%20mastered%20the%20art%20of%20fulfilling%20her%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20requirements%20vis%20a%20vis%20nutrition%20as%20well%20as%20taste%20by%20designing%20her%20own%20menu.%20From%20%3Cem%3Echapatis%20%3C%2Fem%3Einfused%20with%20superfoods%20like%20%3Cem%3Emoringa%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20chutneys%20to%20carry%2C%20Prathima%E2%80%99s%20creative%20juices%20flowed%20for%20her%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20her%20daughter%20went%20to%20the%20US%20to%20pursue%20her%20undergraduate%20degree%2C%20Prathima%20felt%20a%20sense%20of%20vacuum.%20Recognising%20the%20gap%20in%20the%20market%20for%20ready-to-cook%20homemade%20food%2C%20she%20converted%20her%20passion%20for%20cooking%20with%20the%20universal%20need%20for%20quick%20food.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mother%20of%20two%20was%20only%20too%20aware%20of%20the%20struggles%20that%20everyone%20faces%20as%20they%20grapple%20with%20the%20desire%20to%20provide%20homemade%20food%20in%20this%20fast-paced%20world%2C%20where%20time%20constraints%20are%20an%20inescapable%20reality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20turned%20her%20specialised%20recipes%20into%20a%20packaged%20food%20business%20called%20Ammamma%E2%80%99s%20with%20a%20vision%20to