aswat%20swam%20from%20Sri%20Lanka%20to%20India%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaaswat%20Sharma%20(31)%2C%20a%20technical%20architect%2C%20is%20an%20ultra%20long-distance%20swimmer%2C%20triathlete%2C%20national%20water%20polo%20player%2C%20and%20swimmer.%20He%20holds%20all%20India%20records%20and%20over%20500%20medals%20and%20trophies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20athletes%20started%20their%20foray%20into%20athletics%20at%20the%20school%20itself%20and%20participated%20in%20national%20and%20international%20competitions.%20After%20swimming%20in%20events%20around%20the%20world%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20embark%20on%20what%20they%20call%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20the%20toughest%20stretches%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20think%20of%20a%20tough%20swim%2C%20everyone%20always%20mentions%20places%20around%20the%20world%2C%20while%20forgetting%20that%20the%20Ram%20Setu%20stretch%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20difficult.%20Only%20a%20few%20have%20attempted%20and%20completed%20it%2C%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20put%20it%20on%20the%20global%20map%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20idea%20in%20mind%2C%20and%20to%20foster%20positive%20relationships%20between%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20they%20started%20preparations%20in%20earnest%20almost%20three%20years%20back%2C%20says%20the%20swimmer.%20They%20christened%20the%20expedition%20the%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Setu%20Swimming%20Expedition%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20started%20planning%20and%20practising%20for%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20prepared%20in%20different%20water%20and%20weather%20conditions%20with%20an%20experienced%20crew%20guiding%20them%2C%20and%20training%20them%20on%20water%20safety%20and%20preventing%20accidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20of%20their%20practice%20was%20indoors%2C%20swimming%20in%20the%20open%20waters%20was%20a%20completely%20different%20ballgame%2C%20concedes%20Bharat%2C%20which%20accentuates%20the%20need%20for%20better%20infrastructure%20and%20investment%20to%20promote%20such%20sports%20in%20the%20country.%20He%20adds%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286757%2Fpara-swimmer-spina-bifida-breaks-asian-record-niranjan-mukundan-surgeries-medals%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopen-water%20swimming%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20a%20very%20popular%20sport%20in%20India%2C%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20promoted.%20And%20to%20also%20bring%20this%20to%20the%20public%20eye%2C%20the%20duo%20decided%20to%20set%20an%20example%20by%20accomplishing%20this%20incredible%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20efforts%20will%20be%20successful%20when%20we%20see%20more%20young%20talent%20from%20India%20opting%20for%20swimming%20and%20representing%20the%20country%20at%20prestigious%20national%20and%20international%20platforms%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20undertake%20this%20initiative%2C%20the%20swimmers%20received%20permissions%20from%20relevant%20authorities%20like%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20India%20(MEA)%3B%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%2C%20India%20(MoD)%3B%20Ministry%20of%20Health%2C%20India%20(MoHFW)%3B%20High%20Commission%20of%20India%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%3B%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%3B%20and%20other%20Government%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETesting%20your%20mental%20and%20physical%20fitness%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20preparing%20and%20getting%20the%20necessary%20permissions%20from%20the%20two%20Governments%2C%20the%20Navy%20and%20the%20Coast%20Guard%2C%20the%20two%20swimmers%20left%20for%20Sri%20Lanka%20from%20Dhanushkodi%20on%2013%20April%2C%202024%2C%20by%20boat.%20The%20boat%20ride%20itself%20was%20challenging%20and%20led%20to%20severe%20motion%20sickness.%20They%20slept%20on%20the%20boat%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-18-at-11.45.04-min-1713870887-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20duo%20aim%20to%20promote%20adventure%20sports%20and%20open%20water%20swimming%20in%20India.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-18-at-11.45.04-min-1713870887-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-18-at-11.45.04-min-1713870887-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-18-at-11.45.04-min-1713870887-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-18-at-11.45.04-min-1713870887-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-18-at-11.45.04-min-1713870887-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-18-at-11.45.04-min-1713870887-150x200.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-18-at-11.45.04-min-1713870887.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348056%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20duo%20aim%20to%20promote%20adventure%20sports%20and%20open%20water%20swimming%20in%20India.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20spending%20over%2015%20hours%20in%20the%20boat%2C%20they%20started%20their%20swim%20the%20next%20morning%2C%20motivated%20by%20their%20crew%20and%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20Navy.%20The%2032%20km%20swim%20was%20conducted%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20experts%2C%20who%20helped%20the%20swimmers%20navigate%20and%20provided%20nutrition%20during%20the%20swim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20road%20to%20success%20and%20the%20road%20to%20failure%20are%20almost%20exactly%20the%20same.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20practice%2C%20both%20mental%20and%20physical%2C%20along%20with%20belief%20in%20one%E2%80%99s%20ability%20that%20differentiates%20between%20the%20two%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shaaswat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20water%20was%20very%20choppy%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20swim%2C%20unlike%20the%20condition%20they%20had%20practised%20in.%20Yet%2C%20the%20two%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20anything%20deter%20them%20that%20day.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20moments%20when%20you%20can%20lose%20your%20breath%20and%20composure.%20The%20water%20can%20be%20very%20unforgiving.%20You%20face%20certain%20life%20and%20death%20moments%2C%20but%20remember%2C%20that%20you%20must%20respect%20the%20process.%20Take%20the%20leap%20of%20faith%20and%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20move%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20few%20hours%20were%20excruciating%2C%20their%20skin%20was%20completely%20burnt%2C%20the%20water%20rough%2C%20and%20their%20energy%20low.%20They%20kept%20their%20eyes%20on%20the%20prize%20and%20focused%20on%20the%20outcome%2C%20and%20their%20goal%20for%20doing%20this%20swim.%20The%20crew%20also%20kept%20cheering%20and%20motivating%20them%2C%20helping%20them%20navigate%20the%20turbulent%20waters.%20It%20was%20a%20test%20of%20their%20mental%20and%20emotional%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20me%2C%20this%20achievement%20has%20a%20very%20high%20spiritual%20and%20cultural%20significance.%20As%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333570%2Fsachin-nag-won-only-gold-medal-swimming-for-india-at-asian-games-sports-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enational%20swimmer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20have%20participated%20in%20several%20challenges%2C%20but%20crossing%20the%20Ram%20Setu%20is%20one%20for%20the%20country.%20While%20we%20were%20swimming%20the%20stretch%2C%20we%20were%20filled%20with%20mixed%20emotions%2C%20of%20celebrating%20the%20spirit%20of%20universal%20brotherhood%2C%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20calling%20out%20to%20the%20nation%20to%20nurture%20swimming%20as%20a%20key%20sport%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shaaswat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20greeted%20by%20hundreds%20of%20young%20boys%20and%20girls%20at%20Dhanushkodi%2C%20making%20it%20all%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20all%20boils%20down%20to%20proper%20planning%20and%20collaboration.%20If%20you%20dream%20and%20put%20in%20the%20effort%2C%20there%20are%20people%20to%20support%20you.%20Dream%20big%2C%20follow%20your%20passion%2C%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20hesitate%20to%20extend%20your%20voice%20and%20ask%20for%20help.%20We%20need%20more%20youngsters%20getting%20into%20swimming%20as%20a%20sport%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713873383000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-17-at-17.23.18-1-min-1713871081-scaled.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348050%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bharat%20Sachdeva%20and%20Shaaswat%20Sharma%20swam%20non-stop%20across%20the%20challenging%2032%20km%20stretch%20near%20the%20Ram%20Setu%20in%2010%20hours%2030%20minutes.%20Their%20aim%3F%20To%20promote%20adventure%20sports%20and%20open%20swimming%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348050%2Fbharat-sachdeva-shaaswat-sharma-swimmers-palk-strait-ram-setu-india-sri-lanka-open-water-swimming%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sambar%20Powder%20to%20Pav%20Bhaji%20Masala%3A%208%20Organic%20Spice%20Brands%20To%20Choose%20For%20Your%20Kitchen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3C